name: 透
trans:
──
Was that the results just now? On the phone.

name: プロデューサー
text: ──い、いや……！　じゃなくて！\n通過だ、『W.I.N.G.』に出られるぞ……！
trans:
──N──No...! The other way round!
You passed! You can enter W.I.N.G. now...!

name: プロデューサー
text: やったな透……！　ははっ！

name: プロデューサー
text: ──って、どうしたんだ？\nもっと喜んでいいんだぞ！
trans:
──Huh? What's up?
C'mon, this is your chance to be ecstatic!

name: 透
text: 嬉しい\nなんか実感ないだけ
trans:
I'm happy.
It's just not quite real to me yet.

name: プロデューサー
text: あぁ、まぁ……\n俺も実感って言われるとな
trans:
Ah, well, yeah...
Not like I can really say it's sunk in either.

name: 透
text: ──\nそれに、まだてっぺんじゃないし
trans:
──
And in any case, we're still not at the top.

name: 透
trans: ...We have to keep on. Keep climbing.

name: 透
text: もっともっと、たくさんのぼるんでしょ？
trans: Keep climbing and climbing──climb all that we can, right?

name: 透
text: ふふっ\n忙しいね、プロデューサー

name: 透
trans: ──...A lot of happy things are to come, after all.
